sourcesContent: import store from "../store";    import mainApi from "../mainApi";    export default {        name: "Dashboard",        data: () => ({            drawer: false,            left: true,            appList: null,            domains: null        }),        methods: {            logout() {                store.dispatch('logout');                this.$router.push(this.$route.query.redirect || '/login');            },            loadApps() {                console.log("apps");            },            viewApp(app) {                mainApi().get('apps/' + app.name + '/domains', {                }).then(response => {                    console.log(response.data);                }).catch(e => {                    console.log(e);                })            }        },        created() {            mainApi().get('apps', {})                .then(response => {                    this.appList = response.data.apps;                }).catch(e => {                    console.log(e)            });        }    }
